                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of phase change emulsion based on vacuum emulsifying machine",
                    "一种基于真空乳化机的相变乳液的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method of a phase change emulsion based on a vacuum emulsifying machine, and relates to the technical field of phase change emulsion preparation. The vacuum emulsifying machine is provided with a water pot, an oil pot and a homogenizing pot, and the preparation method comprises the following steps: adding deionized water into the water pot, heating, adding a nucleating agent, stirring, adding a molten emulsifier, and continuously stirring to obtain a water phase; adding a phase-change material into the frying pan, and heating to obtain an oil phase; adding the water phase and the oil phase into a homogenizing pot, adding a co-emulsifier, stirring, and vacuumizing to obtain a mixture; and carrying out staged shear mixing on the mixture, stirring at the same time, and after the end, continuously stirring and cooling to obtain the phase-change emulsion. According to the preparation method, the phase change emulsion is prepared based on the vacuum emulsifying machine, the mixed solution with the large particle size is crushed into particles with the micron-sized particle size in the shearing process, emulsification is more uniform, the stability of the phase change emulsion is improved, and the prepared phase change emulsion is excellent in performance and suitable for industrial large-scale production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请公开了一种基于真空乳化机的相变乳液的制备方法，涉及相变乳液制备技术领域。真空乳化机设有水锅、油锅和均质锅，包括以下步骤：在水锅中加入去离子水进行加热，并加入成核剂进行搅拌，再加入融化后的乳化剂，继续搅拌，得到水相；将相变材料加入油锅中进行加热，得到油相；将水相和油相加入均质锅中，并加入助乳化剂，搅拌，同时抽真空，得到混合物；对混合物进行阶段性剪切混合，同时进行搅拌，结束后，继续搅拌冷却，得到相变乳液。本申请基于真空乳化机制备相变乳液，在剪切过程中将较大粒径的混合液破碎成微米级粒径颗粒，使乳化更加均匀，提高了相变乳液的稳定性，所制备的相变乳液性能优良，适用于工业化大规模生产。"
                }
            ]
